Governor Bello Muhammad Matawalle of Zamfara has approved the appointment of Alhaji Shehu Sa’idu Anka as the clerk to the state House of Assembly. Alhaji Shehu Sa’idu will replace Alhaji Isa Abdullahi Bayaro Anka who will now be moved to the office of the Head of Civil Service for re-assignment. The spokesman of the assembly, Mustapha Jafaru Kaura, in a statement, said the appointment of Shehu Sa’idu is based on his track record of service, wealth of experience and dedication to duty. The statement further said the appointment is with immediate effect and wished the new clerk to the House Allah’s guidance. Sokoto Assembly gets substantive Clerk I won’t victimise workers -Gov. Matawalle Gaidam appoints new Chief of Staff Prostate  ENLARGEMENT? Don't Let Your PROSTATE Frustrate You! Here's A Better NATURAL Way To Shrink Your Prostate Enlargement! -No Surgery, -No Drugs. Shrink To Normal In Just 15 Days! Normalize Your Urination And Erection! Just Click To Get It Now!